      "content": "hey can u help me with my anthro paper? i'm stuck on the intro. basically i need to write about the evolution of human social structures, specifically how more \"modern\" and complex civilizations differ from the way \"primitive\" social structures used to work. can u give me a breakdown of those main differences?",
